Dear Dock:  Since you asked me not to write, I thought I would drop you a few lines...Wharf Rat.<br>
How do you derive that I am a &quot;hayseed hick?&quot;  Is it because my brother and I help our father, a doctor of veterinary medicine, harvest hay to feed his cattle?  Or, is it because we cut firewood, so that our mother, who has a master's degree in English can have fuel for her fireplace?  Please define &quot;hayseed hick,&quot; and explain your implied superiority.<br>
Why the reference to bestiality?  Is it from your deep and dark vault of subliminal thoughts?<br>
Where do you get the idea, &quot;Ol Ed taught me how to be a big and brave soldier?&quot;  I nor anyone else has been able to teach you anything!  Certainly, no one has taught you to be a big and brave soldier.  More likely, you have learned on your own... how to be anything but big and brave.  Instead you have evolved into something despicable, rebellious to any type of regimentation, even that which shapes character and gives definition to amiable social interaction.<br>
No, it is not okay for you to call me a &quot;redskin,&quot; &quot;injun,&quot; or &quot;prairie nigger.&quot;  I have not called myself any of those names... but you have!  I don't recall using the word &quot;gook&quot; in addressing anyone.  However, if I did or should... that doesn't give license to anyone else to be a racist.<br>
I did not &quot;invade&quot; this site... I have no more or no less right than anyone else.  As far as finding honest and intellectual  dialog... it does exist on this site, with some exceptions... you being the principal exception.<br>
Through what grandiosity do you perceive yourself to be the &quot;majority&quot; when you are the ONLY coward in the group (not counting &quot;Disappearing Dick&quot;... your new AWOL disciple.)<br>
Instead of refering to me as a &quot;redneck,&quot; why don't you revert to your usual broad brush of racist tactics and simply call me a &quot;red skin?&quot;  That offends me.  Still, I am proud of my heritage and prefer a copper red pigment in my skin, than having a communist red tint to my views and a broad yellow stripe down my back.<br>
I will not respond to the other obvious and implied filth in your above post.<br>
A final honest and intellectual observation, you are not &quot;just another Bozo on the bus,&quot;  YOU are the ONLY Bozo on the bus!<br><br>
Mustang &quot;Attack Helicopter&quot; Two Four<br><br>
P.S.  Please stop refering to Cooke as a &quot;Cracker.&quot;  He is a &quot;War Mongering, Commie Killing, Jarhead Grunt&quot;... try and have some respect!!!!
